00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:57.679
from Jehovah. Do not be afraid for I am with you. Do not be anxious for I am your God. I will

00:13:57.679 --> 00:14:04.480
fortify you. Yes, I will help you. So it's comforting to know that Jehovah doesn't expect

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:10.399
more of us than we're able to accomplish with his help. So that's definitely comforting as we're

00:14:10.399 --> 00:14:14.879
moving forward in this assignment. Well, great scriptural thoughts, Gage. Thank you very

00:14:14.879 --> 00:14:19.200
much for sharing those and both of you brothers for sharing all of your comments with us.

00:14:19.759 --> 00:14:26.000
We love having you on the governing body. And we wish you Jehovah's rich blessing on your

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:34.230
new assignment. It's wonderful to see Jehovah's people busier than ever in Kingdom work.

00:14:34.789 --> 00:14:40.149
